description: Reserved matters application pursuant to outline planning application P081704 detailing 'Appearance' and 'Landscaping' of Phase 2 of the Packington Estate redevelopment.  Phase 2 includes the erection of part 2 to part 6-storey buildings (some with basements) to provide for 142 dwellings comprising: 43 x 1; 57 x 2; 14 x 3; 16 x 4; 6 x 5 bedroom houses/maisonettes/flats; and 6 studio apartments together with D1 (community centre); A1(shop); D1(non-residential Institution); B1(temporary sales office) floorspace and landscaping works, new roads and on-street car parking.
